data.title: Rook Wilkinson Ebling
data.meta_description: Textbook of Dermatology in Two Volumes, Volume One & Volume Two. Second Edition (= Vol. 1 + Vol. 2, 2 Volumes; 2 Bde.) by Arthur Rook, D.S. Wilkinson, F.J.G. Ebling and a great selection of related books, art and collectibles available now at AbeBooks.com.
data.text:
Leinen. Condition: Zufriedenstellend. [antiquar./rar 2. Aufl.!] 2 Bde./2 Volumes(-set); in englischer Sprache/in english. XILV, 2118 S. / xliv, 2118 p. Grün. Ln, goldgepr. Rückentit.Beide Bde. mit Gebrauchsberieb, Kapitale etwas bedrückt, Blöcke fest, ehem. Expll. einer Ärztebibl.; Signaturaufkleber von Tit. entfernt, an diesen Stellen Reminiszenzen, innen gestempelt u. mit Invent.Nr. versehen; Textereiche sauber, keine weiteren Einträge. Wird als Paket verschickt. Versandgewicht/weight ca. 5,9 KG! International shipping: Please ask for the correct shipping costs! Heavy weight.

Tapa dura. Condition: Como nuevo. 2 volúmenes de tapa dura con dorados en un estuche. Como nuevo. En inglés. Volumen 1 con firma anterior propietaria. Fith edition. Edited by Champion, Burton, Ebling. Vol. 1: Introduccion, Epidemiology and Historical Bibliography, Comparative Dermatology, Anatomy and Organization of Human Skin, . Pages 1-776. Vol. 3: Disorders of Skin Colour, Bullous Eruptions, Lichen Planus and Lichenoid Disorders, . Pages 1561-2294. 28,5 x 22,5 cm.

Hardcover. Condition: Good. No Jacket. 4th Edition. Complete 3 volume set of the 4th edition. Ex-library books with stamps, etc; otherwise, VG condition. The covers look great, except for library name is printed in white on the top front edges and heads of the spines of the books. The bindings are tight. The interior pages are clean and unmarked. Electronic delivery tracking will be issued free of charge.

Leinen. 5. Auflage. Edited by R.H. Champion, J.L. Burton, F.j.G. Ebling. Four Volumes in two slipcases. Vol.1: 776, lvii pp.; Vol. 2: 777-1560 pp.; Vol. 3: 1561-2294; Vol. 4: 2295-3160 pp. --- Former library books; Label on covers removed; stamped inside, cyphers; Text clean and sound; only little traces; all over: books in very good condition. slipcases show some wear, but no bumps.(Versandgewicht: Paket) Please ask for the correct shipping costs. Photos available upon request. 0.0.
